        "section": "Bijection",
        "snippet": "is bijective if and only if it is invertible"
      },
      "provenance": "ai-agent1"
    },
    {
      "kind": "proposition",
      "label": "Composition of bijections is bijective",
      "anchor": {
        "section": "Bijection",
        "snippet": "The composition of two bijections is again a bijection"
      },
      "provenance": "ai-agent1"
    },
    {
      "kind": "proposition",
      "label": "Bijections form the symmetric group",
      "anchor": {
        "section": "Bijection",
